==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tetradite
<hw>Tet"ra*dite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Tetrad</er>.]</ety> <def>A person in some way remarkable with regard
to the number four, as one born on the <xex>fourth</xex> day of the
month, or one who reverenced <xex>four</xex> persons in the
Godhead.</def> <rj><au>Smart.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

